data.description: Updated centrally located ranch style home featuring a two car garage, 4 bedrooms, two full bathrooms and privacy fenced back yard. Roof was replaced in 2023. Custom touches throughout the home to include shaker style wood trim with hooks in foyer and wood accent wall to the vaulted ceiling in great room. Main living areas have laminate flooring throughout, carpet in bedrooms. Kitchen offers updated stainless steel appliances and quartz counter tops. 4th bedroom is also the bonus room with closet.
